# License Notice

This repository is a curated documentation corpus mixing original meta-documents,
a small conversion script, and government source publications. Different parts
are licensed differently.

## Scope summary

| Scope | License |
|-------|---------|
| Meta-docs (`README.md`, `INDEX.md`, `INVENTORY.md`, `CONTRIBUTING.md`, `NIS2-light-micro-LMS.md`, and other original markdown authored in this repo) | **CC-BY-4.0** |
| Markdown derivations of government source documents under `**/md/`, plus root `nis2-directive-nl.md` | **CC-BY-4.0** for the conversion/formatting layer; underlying content retains the licensing of the issuing body |
| `convert-corpus.sh` | **MIT** |
| `templates/**` (CSV, XLSX, accompanying handleidingen) | **CC-BY-4.0** |
| Government source documents (PDF and HTML originals under `eu-directives/`, `eu-implementing-regulation/`, `enisa-guidance/`, `nl-wetsvoorstel/`, `nl-amvb-consultatie/`, `nl-amvb-consultatie-wwke/`, `ncsc-nl/`, `eu-cooperation-group/`, and root NL government PDFs/HTML) | Retain the original public-sector licensing of the issuing body (EU Commission, EUR-Lex, Tweede Kamer, internetconsultatie.nl, NCSC.nl, Digital Trust Center, ENISA). Redistributed unmodified for reference. |

If a specific source document conflicts with this notice, the upstream publisher's terms govern that document.

